       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB09100.
      ******************************************************************
      *
      *   Este programa carrega o Ficheiro COF09100 com os Projectos
      *   (COT36_PROJECTS) que estejam Activos (BACTIVE = "A"),
      *   que năo sejam Custos (ICTACUST = "N"), que sejam externos
      *   (IPROJE = "S") e que năo tenham
      *   previsăo de facturaçăo (COT50_INVOICES).
      *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SPECIAL-NAMES. DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT   COF09100-FILE
                    ASSIGN              TO DISK-COF09100
                    ORGANIZATION        IS SEQUENTIAL
                    FILE STATUS         IS VIAW0011-FSTATUS.

      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       FD  COF09100-FILE.
           COPY COCF9100.

      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-SPACES                PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB09100'.
           05 WS-COCF9100               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COF09100'.
           05 WS-ARVT0500               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'ARVT3600'.
           05 WS-COVT3605               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT3605'.
           05 WS-COVT5008               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5008'.
           05 WS-COVT5401               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COVT5401'.
           05 WS-FACTPROJ               PIC  X(10) VALUE 'FACTPROJ'.
           05 WS-CTABELA-PAISES         PIC  X(10) VALUE 'AR047'.
           05 WS-CTABELA-SITUACAO       PIC  X(10) VALUE 'CO152'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE             PIC X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-FACTURAS              PIC 9(01)  VALUE ZEROS.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA       END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD0500    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3605    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5401    END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5008    END-EXEC.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CRS_COT36 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT NIDPROJECTO
                     , CPROJECT
                     , GDESCPROJECT
                     , DBEGINDATE
                     , DENDDATE
                     , NPERCENTALERT
                     , DALERTDATE
                     , CMOEDA
                     , BACTIVE
                     , NBUDGET
                     , PAIS
                     , CLIENTE
                     , LINHANEG
                     , RESPONS
                     , IPROJI
                     , IPROJE
                     , IACHORAS
                     , IADESPESAS
                     , TPPFAT
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , TIPONEG
                     , DADJUDATE
                     , NBUDCTRV
                     , GJUSTORC
                     , COPORTUNITY
                     , DALTSTAT
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , ICTACUST
                  FROM COVT3605_PROJECTS
                 WHERE ICTACUST  = :COCD3605-ICTACUST
                   AND BACTIVE   = :COCD3605-BACTIVE
                   AND IPROJE    = :COCD3605-IPROJE
              ORDER BY ICTACUST
                     , BACTIVE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1100-OPEN-COCF9100
                 THRU 1100-OPEN-COCF9100-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1200-WRITE-HEADER
                 THRU 1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1100-OPEN-COCF9100.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1100-OPEN-COCF9100'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           OPEN OUTPUT COF09100-FILE.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1100-OPEN-COCF9100-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       1200-WRITE-HEADER.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1200-WRITE-HEADER'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Preencher os titulos das colunas da tabela
           STRING 'País;'                   DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Cliente;'                DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Projecto;'               DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Data Abertura;'          DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Data de Fecho;'          DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Budget;'                 DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Situaçăo;'               DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  'Data Emiss. Ult. Fac.'   DELIMITED BY SIZE
                                            INTO COCF9100-RECORD.

           WRITE COCF9100-RECORD.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       1200-WRITE-HEADER-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-OPEN-CURSOR
              THRU 2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2300-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE CRS_COT36
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2100-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2100-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD5008.

           MOVE COCK0002-SIM            TO COCD3605-IPROJE.
           MOVE COCK0002-NAO            TO COCD3605-ICTACUST.
           MOVE COCK0002-BACTIVE-ACTIVO TO COCD3605-BACTIVE.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN CRS_COT36
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3605                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2100-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
                FETCH CRS_COT36
                 INTO :COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO
                    , :COCD3605-CPROJECT
                    , :COCD3605-GDESCPROJECT
                    , :COCD3605-DBEGINDATE
                    , :COCD3605-DENDDATE
                    , :COCD3605-NPERCENTALERT
                    , :COCD3605-DALERTDATE
                    , :COCD3605-CMOEDA
                    , :COCD3605-BACTIVE
                    , :COCD3605-NBUDGET
                    , :COCD3605-PAIS
                    , :COCD3605-CLIENTE
                    , :COCD3605-LINHANEG
                    , :COCD3605-RESPONS
                    , :COCD3605-IPROJI
                    , :COCD3605-IPROJE
                    , :COCD3605-IACHORAS
                    , :COCD3605-IADESPESAS
                    , :COCD3605-TPPFAT
                    , :COCD3605-CUSERID
                    , :COCD3605-HTIMEST
                    , :COCD3605-TIPONEG
                    , :COCD3605-DADJUDATE
                    , :COCD3605-NBUDCTRV
                    , :COCD3605-GJUSTORC
                    , :COCD3605-COPORTUNITY
                    , :COCD3605-DALTSTAT
                    , :COCD3605-CEMPRESA
                    , :COCD3605-ICTACUST
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT3605                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *---
      *--- Acede ao COT50_INVOICES para verificar se existe previsăo de
      *--- facturaçăo para o Projecto (GREFINV = Espaços e DDATAEMISS >=
      *--- Data do Processamento).
      *---
      *--- Se năo encontrar, escreve o Projecto no Ficheiro.
      *---
           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2350-VER-FACTURAS
                 THRU 2350-VER-FACTURAS-EXIT

              IF WS-FACTURAS = ZEROS

                 INITIALIZE COCF9100-RECORD
                 MOVE ALL ';' TO COCF9100-RECORD

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2500-OBTER-PAIS
                       THRU 2500-OBTER-PAIS-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2550-OBTER-SIT
                       THRU 2550-OBTER-SIT-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2600-OBTER-CLIENTE
                       THRU 2600-OBTER-CLIENTE-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2650-OBTER-ULT
                       THRU 2650-OBTER-ULT-EXIT
                 END-IF

                 IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
                    PERFORM 2700-WRITE-COCF9100
                       THRU 2700-WRITE-COCF9100-EXIT
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2300-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2350-VER-FACTURAS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2350-VER-FACTURAS  '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO   TO COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE ETCL0002-DATA-PROCESSO TO WS-DATA-HOJE.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDPROJECTO
                     ,  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  DDATAEMISS
                     ,  GREFINV
                  INTO :COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD5008-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD5008-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD5008-GREFINV
                  FROM  COVT5008_INVOICES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO =  :COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO
                   AND  GREFINV     =  :CON-SPACES
                   AND  DDATAEMISS  >= :WS-DATA-HOJE
                 FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5008                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE 1     TO WS-FACTURAS
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE ZEROS TO WS-FACTURAS
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2350-VER-FACTURAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-OBTER-PAIS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-OBTER-PAIS'           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA-PAISES           TO ARCD0500-CTABELA.
           MOVE COCD3605-PAIS               TO ARCD0500-CCOD.
           MOVE VIATK002-IDIOMA-DFT         TO ARCD0500-CLINGUA.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GDESC
                  INTO :ARCD0500-GDESC
                  FROM  ARVT0500_CODESTABLE
                 WHERE  CTABELA = :ARCD0500-CTABELA
                   AND  CCOD    = :ARCD0500-CCOD
                   AND  CLINGUA = :ARCD0500-CLINGUA
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-ARVT0500                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE ARCD0500-GDESC         TO COCF9100-GPAIS
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD3605-PAIS          TO COCF9100-GPAIS
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-OBTER-PAIS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2550-OBTER-SIT.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2550-OBTER-SIT '           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-CTABELA-SITUACAO         TO ARCD0500-CTABELA.
           MOVE COCD3605-BACTIVE            TO ARCD0500-CCOD.
           MOVE VIATK002-IDIOMA-DFT         TO ARCD0500-CLINGUA.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GDESC
                  INTO :ARCD0500-GDESC
                  FROM  ARVT0500_CODESTABLE
                 WHERE  CTABELA = :ARCD0500-CTABELA
                   AND  CCOD    = :ARCD0500-CCOD
                   AND  CLINGUA = :ARCD0500-CLINGUA
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-ARVT0500                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD3605-BACTIVE       TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-COD
                MOVE ' - '                  TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-SEP
                MOVE ARCD0500-GDESC         TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-DES
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD3605-BACTIVE       TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-COD
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-SEP
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF9100-BACTIVE-DES
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2550-OBTER-SIT-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2600-OBTER-CLIENTE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2600-OBTER-CLIENTE'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-CLIENTE TO COCD5401-CSIGLA.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  GNOME
                  INTO :COCD5401-GNOME
                  FROM  COVT5401_EMPRESAS
                 WHERE  CSIGLA = :COCD5401-CSIGLA
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5401                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                MOVE COCD3605-CLIENTE       TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-COD
                MOVE ' - '                  TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-SEP
                MOVE COCD5401-GNOME         TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-DES
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE COCD3605-CLIENTE       TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-COD
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-SEP
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF9100-CLIENTE-DES
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2600-OBTER-CLIENTE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2650-OBTER-ULT.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2650-OBTER-ULT     '       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO TO COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  IFNULL(MAX(DDATAEMIS2), "0001-01-01")
                  INTO :COCD5008-DDATAEMIS2
                  FROM  COVT5008_INVOICES
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD5008-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE WS-COVT5008                 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                IF COCD5008-DDATAEMIS2 = COCK0002-DATA-MIN
                   MOVE SPACES              TO COCF9100-DULTEMIS
                ELSE
                   MOVE COCD5008-DDATAEMIS2 TO COCF9100-DULTEMIS
                END-IF
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                MOVE SPACES                 TO COCF9100-DULTEMIS
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2650-OBTER-ULT-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-WRITE-COCF9100.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-WRITE-COCF9100'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD3605-NIDPROJECTO        TO COCF9100-PROJECT-COD.
           MOVE ' - '                       TO COCF9100-PROJECT-SEP.
           MOVE COCD3605-CPROJECT           TO COCF9100-PROJECT-DES.

           MOVE COCD3605-DBEGINDATE         TO COCF9100-DBEGINDATE.
           MOVE COCD3605-DENDDATE           TO COCF9100-DENDDATE.
           MOVE COCD3605-NBUDGET            TO COCF9100-NBUDGET.

           WRITE COCF9100-RECORD.

           PERFORM 9030-FSCHECK
              THRU 9039-FSCHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN FS-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE WS-COCF9100            TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0011-FSTATUS       TO AQCW0100-FILE-STATUS
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2700-WRITE-COCF9100-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           CLOSE COF09100-FILE.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0011.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
      ******************************************************************
